creator: Knaken
descriptionHtml:
Knaken is here to change the way you manage your crypto.

Get started today and manage your Bitcoin, Ethereum, Cardano and more. We offer innovative features and a no-nonsense experience, built to make your crypto experience smarter, simpler and more secure.
we make it easy for everyone to get started on our platform, so whether you're dipping your toes in crypto or an active trader, join us. We're glad you're here.

Manage your crypto safely and easily on the Knaken application wherever you are!
This application is an early build. This means that we are actively working on features and improving the application.

Current features:
• Actual prices
• Percentage increase / decrease
• Filter by risers and fallers

More coming soon!

Do you have questions or need help?
Go to Knaken.nl for information and to contact Knaken support.
descriptionShort: Manage your crypto safely & easily at Knaken; the place for beginners & veterans
